libqmail (0.1-6) unstable; urgency=medium

  * First version
  * added tai, taia functions for indimail-mta
  * fixed data type of length argument of stralloc_readyplus(), stralloc_copyb(), stralloc_catb()
  * fixed generation of hasmkffo.h
  * fixed incorrect definitions of signals in sig.h
  * define env_isinit as extern in env.h as it is already defined in env.c
  * added authentication crytographic routines digest_md5, hmac_md5, hmac_ripemd, hmac_sha1, hmac_sha256, hmac_sha512, md5
  * added md5_crypt, sha256_crypt, sha512_crypt
  * added mkpasswd function to generate password

 -- Manvendra Bhangui <manvendra@indimail.org>  Wed, 01 Apr 2020 17:56:50 +0200
